706514f-a.title: Brooklyn: Rockaway Parkway - New York Avenue (East)
706514f-a.text:
Rockway Parkway, east side, at and south of East New York Ave., showing
at the left a frame house No. (1124 East New York Ave)., beyond which is
the 14th Street Subway (B.M.T.) Line.

P. L. Sperr.
